# v0.11.0-rc.2

Please report all bugs in our [Discord server](https://slimevr.dev/discord) for now in the appropriate development channels (`#server`, `#gui`, `#autobone`, etc.). If you need tech support or are not sure if you did find a bug, please use the `#support-forum`.

## Use the installer to install or update!
Use the installer to install or update SlimeVR if you're on Windows. You can find it here:
* Windows web installer: https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Installer/releases/latest/download/slimevr_web_installer.exe
* To run SlimeVR, use the shortcut from the start menu or desktop, or open the installation folder and launch slimevr.exe.

### ~~Flatpak distribution for Linux~~
Flatpak is not being updated because our framework is using an old version of `webkit2gtk` at the moment, we will update it when our framework releases a more stable release that supports a new version.

## What's Changed
* change codeowners by @TheButlah in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/908
* Add a `TrackerStatus.TIMED_OUT` for temporal timeouts by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/903
* Add reboot retries when trying to connect to WiFi by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/907


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/compare/v0.11.0-rc.1...v0.11.0-rc.2

__________

# v0.11.0-rc.1

Please report all bugs in our [Discord server](https://slimevr.dev/discord) for now in the appropriate development channels (`#server`, `#gui`, `#autobone`, etc.). If you need tech support or are not sure if you did find a bug, please use the `#support-forum`.

## Use the installer to install or update!
Use the installer to install or update SlimeVR if you're on Windows. You can find it here:
* Windows web installer: https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Installer/releases/latest/download/slimevr_web_installer.exe
* To run SlimeVR, use the shortcut from the start menu or desktop, or open the installation folder and launch slimevr.exe.

### ~~Flatpak distribution for Linux~~
Flatpak is not being updated because our framework is using an old version of `webkit2gtk` at the moment, we will update it when our framework releases a more stable release that supports a new version.

## What's Changed
* Use Bones by @Louka3000 and @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/787
* Fix 3d preview reset math by @0forks in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/881
* Fix pipe crash when SteamVR fails to boot by @0forks in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/887
* Add new message from firmware for finding server by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/870
* Prompt before closing SlimeVR when trackers are still connected by @Eric13246 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/862
* Update tauri 2 by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/858
* fix nix not using toolchain version by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/857
* add me to codeowners in settings parts of GUI by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/885
* add android CI by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/889
* Skeleton preview by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/817
* Add errors and disabled state to Input by @loucass003 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/879
* Add disabled state to Ratio, Fix typos and bad typing by @loucass003 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/878
* Add more colors to checkbox by @loucass003 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/877
* Fixed appearance on exit warning modal by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/890
* Refactor TrashIcon ArrowIcon and LoaderIcon by @loucass003 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/876
* fix resize glitches by @loucass003 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/874
* Fix VRMode not going back to home screen when resizing to desktop layout by @loucass003 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/873
* Make button and typography children optional by @loucass003 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/872
* Refactor of the dropdown component by @loucass003 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/875
* Kotlin leg tweaks by @Stermere in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/809
* add android to release pipeline by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/891
* New Pontoon translations by @SlimeVR-bot in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/868
* Fix the connected tracker modal not having it's config saved by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/896
* Try forcing manual mounting on setup by @ImUrX and @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/852
* Don't set all trackers to "ok" on device reconnect by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/883
* Add pause tracking keybind & protobuf command by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/867
* Android serial by @loucass003 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/888
* Add default mounting orientation for certain body parts by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/898
* Separate scale from proportions in AutoBone by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/846
* better checks for tracker id on tracker error by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/901

