# v0.10.0

Please report all bugs in our [Discord server](https://slimevr.dev/discord) for now in the appropriate development channels (`#server`, `#gui`, `#autobone`, etc.). If you need tech support or are not sure if you did find a bug, please use the `#support-forum`.

## Use the installer to install or update!
Use the installer to install or update SlimeVR if you're on Windows. You can find it here:
* Windows web installer: https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Installer/releases/latest/download/slimevr_web_installer.exe
* To run SlimeVR, use the shortcut from the start menu or desktop, or open the installation folder and launch slimevr.exe.

### ~~Flatpak distribution for Linux~~
Flatpak is not being updated because our framework is using an old version of `webkit2gtk` at the moment, we will update it when our framework releases a more stable release that supports the new version.

## What's Changed
* Update metainfo by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/834
* Convert HumanSkeleton to Kotlin by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/783
* add import proportions button by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/811
* Make UDPPackets Floats safe by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/832
* Fix config shenanigans by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/836
* knee-ankle interpolation by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/780
* Fix icons and add more & fill in web manifest by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/835
* Track connection by SocketAddress instead of IP address. by @kitlith in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/753
* Resets settings by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/806
* use devenv for nix develop by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/830
* Fix right foot skeleton offset by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/840
* Fix hash diplayName to not change by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/841
* Fix foot tracker orientation by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/843
* Android ByteBuffer and Color fixes by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/842
* Filter out !isSiteLocalAddress from addresses by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/847
* Add _trackerNum to extensions' displaynames by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/848
* Fix RPCUtil not checking for the interface before looking for it by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/849
* feat: use path-alias by @marcozzxx810 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/771
* New Pontoon translations by @SlimeVR-bot in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/839

## Translation changes
* Updated 🇦🇪 Arabic translation (@FennT)
* Updated 🇮🇹 Italian translation (@namakeingo)
* Updated 🇫🇷 French translation (@Louka3000)
* Updated 🇳🇱 Dutch translation (@Smeltie)
* Updated 🇵🇱 Polish translation (@ReDoXpl)
* Updated 🇷🇺 Russian translation (@CheatEvent)
* Updated 🇨🇳 Simplified Chinese translation (@Disappear9)
* Updated 🧋 Traditional Chinese translation (@medicalwei)

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/compare/v0.9.1...v0.10.0

__________

# v0.10.0-rc.2

This is a release candidate. Back up your vrconfig.yml at `%AppData%\dev.slimevr.SlimeVR` before running.
Please report all bugs in our [Discord server](https://slimevr.dev/discord), in the appropriate forum post in `#beta-testing-forum`!

## Installation
* Download the new release below and extract it.
* Replace `slimevr.jar` and `slimevr.exe` in the install folder (`C:\Program Files (x86)\SlimeVR Server`)
* To run SlimeVR, use the shortcut from the start menu or desktop, or open the installation folder and launch slimevr.exe.

## What's Changed
* Fix right foot skeleton offset by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/840
* Fix hash diplayName to not change by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/841
* Fix foot tracker orientation by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/843
* Android ByteBuffer and Color fixes by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/842


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/compare/v0.10.0-rc.1...v0.10.0-rc.2

__________

# v0.10.0-rc.1

This is a release candidate. Back up your vrconfig.yml at `%AppData%\dev.slimevr.SlimeVR` before running.
Please report all bugs in our [Discord server](https://slimevr.dev/discord), in the appropriate forum post in `#beta-testing-forum`!

## Installation
* Download the new release below and extract it.
* Replace `slimevr.jar` and `slimevr.exe` in the install folder (`C:\Program Files (x86)\SlimeVR Server`)
* To run SlimeVR, use the shortcut from the start menu or desktop, or open the installation folder and launch slimevr.exe.

## What's Changed
* Update metainfo by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/834
* Convert HumanSkeleton to Kotlin by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/783
* add import proportions button by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/811
* Make UDPPackets Floats safe by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/832
* Fix config shenanigans by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/836
* knee-ankle interpolation by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/780
* Fix icons and add more & fill in web manifest by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/835
* Track connection by SocketAddress instead of IP address. by @kitlith in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/753
* Resets settings by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/806
* use devenv for nix develop by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/830


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/compare/v0.9.1...v0.10.0-rc.1

__________

# v0.9.1

Please report all bugs in our [Discord server](https://slimevr.dev/discord) for now in the appropriate development channels (`#server`, `#gui`, `#autobone`, etc.). If you need tech support or are not sure if you did find a bug, please use the `#support-forum`.

## Use the installer to install or update!
Use the installer to install or update SlimeVR if you're on Windows. You can find it here:
* Windows web installer: https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Installer/releases/latest/download/slimevr_web_installer.exe
* To run SlimeVR, use the shortcut from the start menu or desktop, or open the installation folder and launch slimevr.exe.

### ~~Flatpak distribution for Linux~~
Flatpak is not being updated because our framework is using a old version of `webkit2gtk` at the moment, we will update it when our framework releases a more stable release that supports the new version of it.

## What's Changed
* Update to tauri 2 by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/665
* Minor: Updated battery indicator V placement by @MakerKath in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/810
* Improve HMD handling by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/801
* Fix acceleration adjustement and add to visualizer by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/804
* Improve debugging experience by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/790
* Fix UDP timeout overriding error status by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/812
* Fix Tauri 2 update by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/813
* Fix OSCTrackers yawAlign by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/818
* Fix nix with latest rust update by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/820
* Fix HMD designation by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/821 
* Fix tauri 2 again by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/827
* Fix receiving OSC by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/825
* Fix the offsets of arms from controllers by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/826
* Add FT232 Serial Chipset to the known list by @unlogisch04 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/823
* Small fixes pt. 3 by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/822
* Small GUI fixes, pt. 2 by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/815
* tauri should work now by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/831

## Translation changes
* Updated 🧋 Traditional Chinese translation (@medicalwei)
* Updated 🇨🇳 Simplified Chinese translation (@Disappear9)
* Updated 🇵🇱 Polish translation (@MenacingExiler @ReDoXpl)
* Updated 🇳🇱 Dutch translation (@RatDotRaw @Smeltie)
* Updated 🇰🇷 Korean translation (@Kamilake)
* Updated 🇦🇪 Arabic translation (@FennT)
* Updated 🇫🇷 French translation (@Louka3000 @SlimePuppyRR)
* Updated 🌎 Latinamerican Spanish translation (@ImUrX)
* Updated 🇪🇸 Spain Spanish translation (@Faxty-sudo)
* Updated 🇪🇪 Estonian translation (@mikkmer)
* Updated 🇫🇮 Finish translation (@siofrain @valzzu)
* Updated 🇷🇺 Russian translation (@CheatEvent)
* Updated 🥺 Engwish translation (@ButterscotchV)
* Updated 🇦🇪 Arabic translation (@FennT @RichardTello123)
* Updated 🇮🇹 Italian translation (@namakeingo)

## New Contributors
* @MakerKath made their first contribution in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/810
* @Smeltie made their first contribution in #807 
* @SlimePuppyRR made their first contribution in #828 
* @mikkmer made their first contribution in #828 
* @valzzu made their first contribution in #828 
* @CheatEvent made their first contribution in #828 
* @RichardTello123 made their first contribution in #828 

