# v0.9.0-rc.1

This is a release candidate.
Please report all bugs in [Discord](https://slimevr.dev/discord), in the appropriate forum post in `#beta-testing-forum`!

## Installation
* Download the new release below and extract it.
* Replace `slimevr.jar` and `slimevr.exe` in the install folder (`C:\Program Files (x86)\SlimeVR Server`)
* To run, open SlimeVR folder and launch slimevr.exe, or use shortcut from start menu or desktop

## What's Changed
* Don't log non-imu trackers' drift by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/759
* Separate the server in subprojects by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/727
* Manual mounting overhaul by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/745
* Mocap mode by @Stermere in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/749
* Prioritize non-computed head tracker by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/751
* Don't create new skeletons by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/761
* fix: filter non imu in connected tracker by @marcozzxx810 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/763
* Add rust file logging by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/752
* Move SteamVR code to desktop subproject by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/755
* Fix Scroll on mobile by @loucass003 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/785
* Add me to GUI codeowners by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/782
* Update appstream metadata by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/762
* Save config and logs on appdata folder by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/770
* Better tap detection by @Stermere in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/778
* Add accessibility settings by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/774
* Fix CI release bundling by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/777
* Improvements on the Autobone GUI by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/776
* Refresh headShift when setting trackers by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/781
* Make displayName consistent via hash by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/775
* Bundle & Receive OSCTrackers by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/773
* Drift compensation tracker and HMD requirement by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/750
* Clarify "extended" skeleton toggles in GUI by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/779
* make sentences consistents by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/789
* Autobone config migration is in wrong version by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/792
* Fix comment on the wrong line by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/791
* Fix toe snap by @Stermere in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/793
* Make manual proportion list grow if there is space by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/784
* Improve defaults SkeletonValues & add ratios in gui by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/743
* Send any computed tracker via VMC for props by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/719
* fix upper chest mounting null by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/799
* Quick fix for BVH issues by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/798
* Fix updateTrackersDriftCompensation condition by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/796
* Move serial communication to desktop subproject by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/756
* Fix tap to assign and other bugs by @Stermere in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/795


