# v0.8.1

Please report all bugs in [Discord](https://slimevr.dev/discord) for now in the ``#support-forum`` forum! Please send all GUI problems to ``#gui`` channel! Help and support for VRChat's OSCTrackers is in ``#vrchat-osctrackers`` channel.

## Use the installer to install or update!
Use an installer to install or update SlimeVR if you're on Windows. You can find it here:
* Windows web installer: https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Installer/releases/latest/download/slimevr_web_installer.exe
* To run, open SlimeVR folder and launch slimevr.exe, or use shortcut from start menu or desktop

### ~~Flatpak distribution for Linux~~
Flatpak is not being updated because our framework is using a old version of `webkit2gtk` at the moment, we will update it when our framework releases a more stable release that supports the new version of it.

## What's Changed
* Clear recent Pontoon untranslated keys by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/741
* Fix VRChat OSC Trackers' reset by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/742
* Stop unconditionally hogging serial ports by @evg-zhabotinsky in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/692
* Fix mobile bugs by @ImUrX and @loucass003 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/740
* Make AutoBone more modular and readable by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/684
* Fix Dropdown not opening by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/744
* mobile body proportions by @loucass003 and @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/718
* Add upper chest tracking point by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/716
* Acceleration alignment fix by @Stermere, @Louka3000 and @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/737
* Don't ask twice to reset non-imu trackers by @Louka3000 and @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/760
* Improve Autobone upperChest and fix VMC upperChest by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/754
* New Pontoon translations by @SlimeVR-bot in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/739

### Translation changes
* **Added :ukraine: Ukrainian translation (@Noted5 @nyarl)**
* Updated :united_arab_emirates: Arabic translation (@FennT)
* Updated :czech_republic: Czech translation (@Arxari)
* Updated :de: German translation (@TheDevMinerTV @unlogisch04 @ZahnatomLetsPlay)
* Updated :greece: Greek translation (@namakeingo @ody007gr)
* Updated :fr: French translation (@Louka3000)
* Updated :cn: Simplified Chinese translation (@Disappear9)
* Updated :brazil: Brazilian Portuguese translation (@Gaabbu)
* Updated :jp: Japanese translation (@sorenxysm @yenmax @Sorakage033)
* Updated :poland: Polish translation (@ReDoXpl)
* Updated :ru: Russian translation (@Hornil @SummerArtz)
* Updated :thailand: Thai translation (@MausyMaz)
* Updated :bubble_tea: Traditional Chinese translation (@medicalwei)
* Updated :netherlands: Dutch translation (@Vyolex)
* Updated :kr: Korean translation (@Kamilake)
* Updated :tr: Turkish translation (@phoebeyay @TheStupidGuy21)
* Progressing on Hebrew translation (@namakeingo)


