# v0.8.0

Please report all bugs in [Discord](https://slimevr.dev/discord) for now in the ``#support-forum`` forum! Please send all GUI problems to ``#gui`` channel! Help and support for VRChat's OSCTrackers is in ``#vrchat-osctrackers`` channel.

## Use the installer to install or update!
Use an installer to install or update SlimeVR if you're on Windows. You can find it here:
* Windows web installer: https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Installer/releases/latest/download/slimevr_web_installer.exe
* To run, open SlimeVR folder and launch slimevr.exe, or use shortcut from start menu or desktop

### ~~Flatpak distribution for Linux~~
Flatpak is not being updated because our framework is using a old version of `webkit2gtk` at the moment, we will update it when our framework releases a more stable release that supports the new version of it.

## What's Changed
* fix left foot icon being reversed by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/672
* Improve vrchat osctrackers text by @Louka3000 and @ButterscotchV  in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/675
* Update VRServer.java with important change by @TheButlah in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/685
* More GUI fixes by @ImUrX and @ButterscotchV  in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/678
* Update contributing information in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/673 (@Louka3000 @ButterscotchV @ImUrX)
* Trackers rewrite & Switch to new math lib in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/647 (@Louka3000 @ButterscotchV @ImUrX)
* Convert UDP Server stuff to Kotlin in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/683 (@ImUrX @Louka3000)
* Tap setup by @ImUrX and @Stermere  in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/667
* Fix the reason of my suffering by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/693
* Calibration tutorial by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/687
* Basic version update checking by @Louka3000  and @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/690
* Additional Theme Options by @NWBx01 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/671
* Log yaw drift and reset all trackers by @Louka3000 and @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/682
* New Pontoon translations by @SlimeVR-bot in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/659
* Fix legtweaks knees condition by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/702
* Fix BVH translation comment by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/698
* Add classpath minimization by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/700
* Require the use of run command for running server by @ImUrX and @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/701
* Better foot plant by @Stermere in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/691
* Add tracking pausing by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/697
* Status system by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/689
* Some more random improvements by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/695
* Fix user height calculation and AutoBone targetHeight initialization order by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/705
* Send Tracker Battery Info to SteamVR in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/668 (@NWBx01 @Louka3000 @ImUrX)
* Add more tutorials on setup by @ImUrX and @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/696
* Fix GUI bugs by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/707
* Add niche option to always use floorclip by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/710
* Fix bundling for mac by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/711
* Fix Nix script not building by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/714
* Update dependencies and stuff by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/704
* Mobile gui basics in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/713 (@loucass003 @TheDevMinerTV @ImUrX)
* Small mobile gui Fixes by @loucass003 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/720
* Fix player trackers not being found or assigned in HumanSkeleton by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/722
* Do Not Send Erroneous Battery Readings to SteamVR by @NWBx01 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/712
* New Pontoon translations by @SlimeVR-bot in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/703
* Potential floorclip fixes by @Stermere in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/728
* Fix allowDriftCompensation setting to false on mounting or assign by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/717
* Tracking pause fixes by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/721
* Fix reset status on yaw reset by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/730
* fix trackerName logic for error status by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/715
* Rename save proportions to export proportions by @Vyolex in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/732
* PoseFrame fix & AutoBone change by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/736
* Updates the recommended mounting method to manual by @Vyolex in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/734
* fix trackerError status returning empty object on null device by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/735
* Finally fix small window by @ImUrX and @Pixel6554 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/731
* New Pontoon translations by @SlimeVR-bot in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/738

### Translation changes
* **Added :denmark: Danish translation (@RXRESaccharine @viwas45hu978ot)**
* Updated :netherlands: Dutch translation (@Vyolex)
* Updated :it: Italian translation (@namakeingo @Etch9)
* Updated :fr: French translation (@Louka3000 @The1Pigeon @Toonmomo @jojos38)
* Updated :united_arab_emirates: Arabian translation (@FennT)
* Updated :pleading_face: Engwish translation (@ButterscotchV)
* Updated :cn: Simplified Chinese translation (@Disappear9 @medicalwei @Anteness)
* Updated :de: German translation (@unlogisch04 @TheDevMinerTV)
* Updated :kr: Korean translation (@Kamilake)
* Updated :ru: Russian translation (@Hornil)
* Updated :bubble_tea: Traditional Chinese translation (@yenmax @medicalwei)
* Updated :poland: Polish translation (@ReDoXpl)
* Updated :finland: Finish translation (@siofrawell)
* Updated :de: German translation (@TheDevMinerTV @RexVizsla @Piranja81)
* Updated :earth_americas: Latinamerican Spanish translation (@ArcTheArc @ImUrX)
* Updated :jp: Japanese translation (@sorenxysm)
* Started :thailand: Thai translation (@MausyMaz)

