# v0.7.1

Please report all bugs in [Discord](https://slimevr.dev/discord) for now in the ``#support-forum`` forum! Please send all GUI problems to ``#gui`` channel! Help and support for VRChat's OSCTrackers is in ``#vrchat-osctrackers`` channel.

## Use the installer to install or update!
Use an installer to install or update SlimeVR if you're on Windows. You can find it here:
* Windows web installer: https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Installer/releases/latest/download/slimevr_web_installer.exe
* To run, open SlimeVR folder and launch slimevr.exe, or use shortcut from start menu or desktop

### Flatpak distribution for Linux
Now you can install [SlimeVR from Flathub](https://flathub.org/apps/details/dev.slimevr.SlimeVR) and update it through there. You can install it by running: ``flatpak install flathub dev.slimevr.SlimeVR``

## Changelog since v0.7.0
* Change AutoBone's decay function to be more standard by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/630
* Make config migration more robust by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/670


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/compare/v0.7.0...v0.7.1

__________

# v0.7.0

Please report all bugs in [Discord](https://slimevr.dev/discord) for now in the ``#support-forum`` forum! Please send all GUI problems to ``#gui`` channel! Help and support for VRChat's OSCTrackers is in ``#vrchat-osctrackers`` channel.

## Use the installer to install or update!
Use an installer to install or update SlimeVR if you're on Windows. You can find it here:
* Windows web installer: https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Installer/releases/latest/download/slimevr_web_installer.exe
* To run, open SlimeVR folder and launch slimevr.exe, or use shortcut from start menu or desktop

### Flatpak distribution for Linux
Now you can install [SlimeVR from Flathub](https://flathub.org/apps/details/dev.slimevr.SlimeVR) and update it through there. You can install it by running: ``flatpak install flathub dev.slimevr.SlimeVR``

## Changelog since v0.6.3
* New Pontoon translations by @SlimeVR-bot in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/597
* server: Fix frame drops in SteamVR/Windows by @0forks in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/607
* VMC Support by @Louka3000, @ButterscotchV and @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/606
* Use CSS selectors instead of an if in react for MainLayout buttons by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/605
* server: Log resets from all sources by @0forks in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/604
* Convert AutoBone to Kotlin and extend PoseFrame data functionality by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/581
* Add prettier to check formatting during CI linting by @TheDevMinerTV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/557
* Fix vrconfig crashing on load by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/613
* [GUI] Improve window resizing behavior by @TheButlah in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/616
* Convert AutoBone config to Kotlin and fix config loading by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/614
* Toesnap and Footplant by @Stermere in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/609
* [ImgBot] Optimize images by @imgbot in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/618
* Rename resets by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/611
* Add a ratio mode for manual offsets by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/615
* feat: feedback sound when reset triggered by @marcozzxx810 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/576
* New Pontoon translations by @SlimeVR-bot in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/608
* server: Implement non-blocking IO for VR bridges by @0forks in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/629
* gui: Volume slider for feedback sound by @0forks in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/638
* Fixes for sound feedback PR by @0forks in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/637
* Fix skeleton config loading by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/635
* Disable leg tweaks on proportions by @Stermere in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/627
* Separate MacOS artifact and label Windows artifact by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/640
* Update AutoBone steps on the GUI to match the docs by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/636
* Increase maximum smoothing by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/643
* WiFi provisioning and serial fixes by @Eirenliel, @ImUrX and @TheDevMinerTV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/590
* Mounting reset improvements by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/641
* Improve setup wizard by @ImUrX, @Spazznyan, @ButterscotchV and @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/639
* Revert VRServer tick interval by @0forks in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/644
* Disable skeleton visualizer by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/646
* Start including media framework on appimage by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/650
* Simplify code and fix Android crash by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/645
* Fix default tracker mounting state to be front correctly by @Eirenliel in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/651
* Add more style to the GUI with icons by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/652
* Fix TPS display for devices with >1 tracker by @0forks in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/657
* Replace butt icon by hip by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/658
* New Pontoon translations by @SlimeVR-bot in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/633
* Fix AutoBone wording (not an AI ;3) by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/661
* Fix lower arm icon being hidden to the right by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/660
* [ImgBot] Optimize images by @imgbot in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/662
* Repair icons for linux by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/664
* Theme support by @ImUrX and @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/663
* feat: VRServer gracefully shutdown by @marcozzxx810 and @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/632

### Translation changes
* Updated :netherlands: Dutch translation (@Vyolex @namakeingo)
* Updated :it: Italian translation (@namakeingo @Etch9)
* Updated :earth_americas: Latinamerican Spanish translation (@ImUrX @ArcTheArc)
* Updated :fr: French translation (@Louka3000 @The1Pigeon)
* Updated :brazil: Brazilian Portuguese translation (@Gaabbu)
* Updated :united_arab_emirates: Arabian translation (@FennT)
* Updated :pleading_face: Engwish translation (@ButterscotchV @namakeingo @SummerArtz)
