# v0.6.3

Please report all bugs in [Discord](https://slimevr.dev/discord) for now in the ``#support-forum`` forum! Please send all GUI problems to ``#gui`` channel! Help and support for VRChat's OSCTrackers is in ``#vrchat-osctrackers`` channel.

## Use the installer to install or update!
Use an installer to install or update SlimeVR if you're on Windows. You can find it here:
* Windows web installer: https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Installer/releases/latest/download/slimevr_web_installer.exe
* To run, open SlimeVR folder and launch slimevr.exe, or use shortcut from start menu or desktop

### Flatpak distribution for Linux
Now you can install [SlimeVR from Flathub](https://flathub.org/apps/details/dev.slimevr.SlimeVR) and update it through there. You can install it by running: ``flatpak install flathub dev.slimevr.SlimeVR``

## Changelog since v0.6.2 (unsorted)
* hide overlay when no initial response fronm it by @loucass003 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/600
* Fix hip interpolation by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/603
* Make offset go the right direction by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/602
* fix row height by @loucass003 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/601
* Start using localStorage for config by @ImUrX and @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/598
* Upload artifacts to draft when new tag by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/599


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/compare/v0.6.2...v0.6.3

__________

# v0.6.2

Please report all bugs in [Discord](https://slimevr.dev/discord) for now in the ``#support-forum`` forum! Please send all GUI problems to ``#gui`` channel! Help and support for VRChat's OSCTrackers is in ``#vrchat-osctrackers`` channel.

## Use the installer to install or update!
Use an installer to install or update SlimeVR if you're on Windows. You can find it here:
* Windows web installer: https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Installer/releases/latest/download/slimevr_web_installer.exe
* To run, open SlimeVR folder and launch slimevr.exe, or use shortcut from start menu or desktop

### Flatpak distribution for Linux
Now you can install [SlimeVR from Flathub](https://flathub.org/apps/details/dev.slimevr.SlimeVR) and update it through there. You can install it by running: ``flatpak install flathub dev.slimevr.SlimeVR``

## Changelog since v0.6.1
* New Pontoon translations by @SlimeVR-bot in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/586
* Add more tracker info by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/596
* Load default values and toggles by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/595
* Add linux feeder socket by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/592
* Use hands everywhere instead of controller by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/588
* Catch Tauri stuff so web version doesn't suffer by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/587

### Translation changes
* Updated :netherlands: Dutch translation (@Vyolex)
* Updated :it: Italian translation (@namakeingo)
* Updated :earth_americas: Latinamerican Spanish translation (@MaxEvil47)
