# v0.6.1

Please report all bugs in [Discord](https://slimevr.dev/discord) for now in the ``#support-forum`` forum! Please send all GUI problems to ``#gui`` channel! Help and support for VRChat's OSCTrackers is in ``#vrchat-osctrackers`` channel.

## Use the installer to install or update!
Use an installer to install or update SlimeVR if you're on Windows. You can find it here:
* Windows web installer: https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Installer/releases/latest/download/slimevr_web_installer.exe
* To run, open SlimeVR folder and launch slimevr.exe, or use shortcut from start menu or desktop

### Flatpak distribution for Linux
Now you can install [SlimeVR from Flathub](https://flathub.org/apps/details/dev.slimevr.SlimeVR) and update it through there. You can install it by running: ``flatpak install flathub dev.slimevr.SlimeVR``

## Changelog since v0.6.0:

### Unsorted
* Add User Action packet. Allows for reset buttons on trackers and not just tap detection to reset. by @carl-anders in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/457
* Finished relicense by @TheButlah in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/428
* Offsets refactor + add chest offset by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/443
* Improve config reliability by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/476
* gui: Fix UI wrapping in settings by @0forks in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/467
* Support arbitrary sensor id's for devices by @carl-anders in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/464
* gui: Fix websocket send crash on reconnect by @0forks in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/463
* server: Send accel and ref-adjusted rotations by @0forks in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/449
* Do actions on creation of tag/branch by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/454 
* Use `cache-apt-pkgs-action` for apt instead by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/474
* Fix drift compensation affecting reset and fast resets by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/471
* Add .editorconfig by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/469
* Bring back elbow offset by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/470
* gui: More info in tracker table and IMU visualizer by @0forks in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/450
* Add `BVHSettings` and allow writing end nodes by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/483
* send messages to steamvr-driver on linux by @FredrikHson in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/489
* Improve reset code and make it so VRTrackers can reset by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/480
* gui: Fix battery indicator always full by @0forks in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/492
* Let code owners merge PRs by @Eirenliel in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/479
* Better JVM detection by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/494
* Fix osctracker id going out of bound by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/512
* Mirror tracker assignment by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/518
* Maintain compatibility with Java 19 by @Kamilake in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/508
