* Make battery percentage persist after tracker disconnect by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/536
* Configure user for rebase script by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/535
* Add a "clear drift compensation" button by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/505
